1. Add Web Scraper extention in chrome
   https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/web-scraper/jnhgnonknehpejjnehehllkliplmbmhn

2. Open in chrome the forum webpage: https://forum.allianz.de/hilfe/kfz-versicherung

3. Press F12 to open Developer tools

4. Click on the Web Scraper menu

5. Click on the "Create new Sitemap" option

6. Click on the "import Sitemap" option

7. Copy and paste the content below into the Sitemap JSON area

