8. (Optional) If you want, you can rename the sitemap writing a new name in the "Reanme Sitemap" field

9. Click on the "Import Sitemap" button to import the BonusDrive forum's scraper

10. Click on the Sitemap forum-allianz (or the name that you chose in 8)

11. Click on the scrape option and choose the "Request interval" and "Page load delay". We recommend to put these values on 2000

12. Click on Start scraping to start the scraper process. Wait for a couple of minutes until the scraper process finishes

13. After finishing the scraper process, you can export the extracted data (*.cvs) from "Sitemap forum-allianz" -> "Export data as CSV" 